gramming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/MotorControllerSupply.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/MotorControllerSupply-1024x470.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3906\" width=\"417\" height=\"190\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/MotorControllerSupply-1024x470.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/MotorControllerSupply-300x138.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/MotorControllerSupply-150x69.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/MotorControllerSupply.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 417px) 100vw, 417px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h4>Analog Encoders<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Next connect the four <strong>Analog Encoder<\/strong> cables to the two <strong>Microcontrollers <\/strong>as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/AnalogEncoderConnections.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/AnalogEncoderConnections-1024x511.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3926\" width=\"435\" height=\"217\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/AnalogEncoderConnections-1024x511.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/AnalogEncoderConnections-300x150.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/AnalogEncoderConnections-150x75.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/AnalogEncoderConnections-768x383.jpg 768w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/AnalogEncoderConnections.jpg 1092w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 435px) 100vw, 435px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h4>Drive Motors<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Then connect the four <strong>Quadrature Encoder<\/strong> cables for the <strong>Drive Motors<\/strong> as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/DriveMotorEncoderConnections-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/DriveMotorEncoderConnections-1-1024x927.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3932\" width=\"563\" height=\"509\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/DriveMotorEncoderConnections-1-1024x927.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/DriveMotorEncoderConnections-1-300x272.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/DriveMotorEncoderConnections-1-150x136.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/DriveMotorEncoderConnections-1-768x695.jpg 768w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/DriveMotorEncoderConnections-1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 563px) 100vw, 563px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now feed the <strong>Drive Motor Power<\/strong> wires through the <strong>Swerve Base<\/strong> and connect them to the <strong>Motor Controllers<\/strong> as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/DriveMotorPowerConnections.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/DriveMotorPowerConnections-1024x1001.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3936\" width=\"549\" height=\"536\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/DriveMotorPowerConnections-1024x1001.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/DriveMotorPowerConnections-300x293.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/DriveMotorPowerConnections-150x147.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/DriveMotorPowerConnections-768x751.jpg 768w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/DriveMotorPowerConnections.jpg 1082w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 549px) 100vw, 549px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Note that the order in which you connect the power wires to the <strong>Motor Controller<\/strong> is not critical. Connecting them as shown is preferred but if you connect them backwards it merely means that the motors will run in the opposite direction. This can be corrected in software by calling the <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"\/RobotCoreDoc\/classrobot_core_1_1_smart_motor.html#a1880600586c2d55a8acd9d2b13d13097\" target=\"_blank\">setInverted<\/a> function for the motor.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Motor Controllers<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>First connect the four <strong>Motor Controller Cables<\/strong> to the <strong>Motor Controllers<\/strong> as shown below:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControllersConnection.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControllersConnection-1024x998.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3944\" width=\"402\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControllersConnection-1024x998.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControllersConnection-300x293.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControllersConnection-150x146.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControllersConnection-768x749.jpg 768w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControllersConnection.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 402px) 100vw, 402px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>When connecting them, make sure that the edge you marked in white when you created the cables is oriented properly as shown below. If you get this reversed, then the <strong>Drive Motor<\/strong> will be switched with the <strong>Steering Motor.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControllerOrientation.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControllerOrientation.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3945\" width=\"223\" height=\"196\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControllerOrientation.jpg 492w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControllerOrientation-300x263.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControllerOrientation-150x132.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 223px) 100vw, 223px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Then connect the other end of the <strong>Motor Controller Cables<\/strong> to the <strong>Microcontrollers <\/strong>as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControlConnection.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControlConnection-1024x515.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3947\" width=\"535\" height=\"268\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControlConnection-1024x515.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControlConnection-300x151.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControlConnection-150x75.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControlConnection-768x386.jpg 768w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MotorControlConnection.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 535px) 100vw, 535px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h4>Gyro<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Now connect use the<strong> Gyro Cable<\/strong> to connect the <strong>Gyro <\/strong>to the <strong>Microcontroller <\/strong>as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/GyroWiring.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/GyroWiring.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3951\" width=\"356\" height=\"276\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/GyroWiring.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/GyroWiring-300x233.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/GyroWiring-150x116.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/GyroWiring-768x596.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 356px) 100vw, 356px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h4>Main Power \/ Microcontroller Power<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Connect the Main Power and the Microcontroller Power as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MainMicrocontrollerPower.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MainMicrocontrollerPower.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3959\" width=\"587\" height=\"299\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MainMicrocontrollerPower.jpg 927w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MainMicrocontrollerPower-300x153.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MainMicrocontrollerPower-150x76.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/MainMicrocontrollerPower-768x391.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 587px) 100vw, 587px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>You can <a href=\"\/testing-the-wiring-2\/\" data-type=\"page\">Test The Wiring<\/a> for the chassis now, or you can wait and do all of the testing once the shooter is complete.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"\/assembling-the-shooter\/\" data-type=\"